    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition \u2014 a project car or parts vehicle that requires significant attention before it can be considered reliable transportation. The exterior shows substantial wear, including visible rust, dents, and faded or damaged paint that goes well beyond typical cosmetic blemishes. The interior is worn and shows signs of neglect, with damaged upholstery, non-functional components, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues that will require serious repair work \u2014 it is not currently suitable for daily driving and should be approached as a restoration or parts-sourcing opportunity. Buyers should be prepared to invest considerable time and money beyond the purchase price. This listing is best suited for experienced mechanics, hobbyists, or those seeking specific components.",
